<ab facs="#facs_502_r3l22">
<add><ab facs="#facs_502_r2l1">hab mıt hannſen </ab><ab facs="#facs_502_r2l2">von Romrod von </ab><ab facs="#facs_502_r2l3"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒureden </ab></add> vnd ~ der von <expan>Eyſemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Romrods <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> yecʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_502_r3l23">geſagt / vnd eẅr gnade . <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> von <expan>Eyſemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> eẅr <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab>
