<ab facs="#facs_502_r3l26"><expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt <expan>gancʒe<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſʒ / Nu ſol eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> </ab>
