</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_502" id="250r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Johans<ex>en</ex></expan>, bischof zu
                            <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat, wie <add>ewr gnade</add> dem von
                                <expan>Eysemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> vormals
                            <expan>geschribe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>hab, mit Hannsen von Romrod von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu reden</add>, und der von
                                <expan>Eysemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan> Romrods <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
                        yecz gesagt und ewr gnade <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>Eysemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> ewr
                            <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>ernstlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> und dem von Romrod auch
                                <expan>eygentlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geschribe<ex>n</ex></expan> habt etc., das
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und danken des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz.
                        Nu sol ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir von keinr fehe noch von
                                <expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan> spruch
                        <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, die <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> von
                        Romrod zu uns hab. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>ewr</expan> gnade, uns in
                                <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> sachen ewr gnade und guten willen
                        dest <expan>gnediklich<ex>er</ex></expan> zu
                            <expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan> und, was <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add>fürter</add> zu <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>de</expan>, uns das <add>aber</add>
<expan>zu verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> und <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zu lass<ex>en</ex></expan> als etc. <pb facs="#facs_503" id="250v"/>Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>nati<ex>vi</ex>tat<ex>is</ex></expan> Marie
                            <expan>virg<ex>in</ex>is</expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula">
<ab>Cetula: <expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir haben dem
                            <expan>gegenw<ex>er</ex>tigen</expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> das lon geben.</ab>
</div>
